illating solutions to equilibrium\nsolutions. This suggests that the delay is a very important fact which should\nnot be missed in HIV-1 modelling.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 16 Mar 2014 20:25:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Apr 2014 16:05:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-04-10"}
